spite being beloved by critics, with Dearden's work positively reviewed, it was canceled after one season.\n\nIn 2017, Dearden appeared in the film The Last Champion, which stars Cole Hauser as former Olympic wrestler John Wright.\n\nIn 2018, Dearden appeared in season two of the Netflix mockumentary American Vandal, where she played the character Chloe Lyman, acting alongside co-stars Tyler Alvarez, Griffin Gluck, and Travis Tope.","name":"Taylor Dearden","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"BY","iso_639_1":"be","name":"беларуская мова","english_name":"Belarusian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Тэйлар Дірдэн","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"泰勒·德尔登","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"泰勒·德爾登","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Тейлор Дирден","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"טיילור דירדן","primary":false}}]}},"tv_270420_keywords":{"at":1774377002229,"data":{"id":270420,"results":[{"name":"romcom","id":9799},{"name":"gumiho","id":273025},{"name":"fantasy","id":293198}]}},"person_3807617_translations":{"at":1774377012007,"data":{"id":3807617,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Choi Gyu-ri (born 19 July 2000) is an actress, known for Marry My Husband (2024), Happy Battle (2023) and Rookie Cops (2022).","name":"Choi Gyu-ri","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"崔奎莉","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"최규리","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"